    global update
    global ix, iy
    global click_count
    global cor

    ix, iy = event.xdata, event.ydata
    coords = [(ix, iy)]

    cor.append(coords)

    click_count += 1
    if click_count > 1:
        click_count = 0
        cor1 = cor.pop()
        cor2 = cor.pop()

        distance = (cor1[0][0] - cor2[0][0])**2 + (cor1[0][1] - cor2[0][1])**2

        print('distance = ', distance)
        jump(distance)
        update = True
